criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients aged 18 to 75 years;

          -  Patients with non-segmental vitiligo;

          -  Patients with plaque psoriasis;

          -  Patients with atopic dermatitis;

          -  Patients with alopecia areata sclerosis;

          -  written consent, free, informed and signed by the patient and the investigator (before
             any examination required by the study);

          -  Subject affiliated or beneficiary of a social security system.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with segmental vitiligo

          -  Patients under local treatment (topical corticosteroid-Calcineurin inhibitor) for less
             than two weeks.

          -  Patients on therapy, systemic treatments: acitretin, methotrexate, cyclosporine,
             Apremilast, infliximab, adalimumab, etanercept, ustekinumab, secukinumab, ixekizumab,
             dupilumab) for less than 4 weeks.

          -  Pregnant or breastfeeding women

          -  Patient (e) under guardianship

          -  Patient (e) Non-affiliated (e) a social protection
